-dqJZss kxJFgY pf-135_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-ctLKXW gOsYRG pf-136_"><div class="sc-feUYzb iXyfoG pf-137_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dWZrec gFZrdc pf-138_"><p class="sc-ePDMnc dIqczD pf-139_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-d917bb87-7eef-4b60-bec0-327c604e5e52"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Establishes workplace conditions, sanitation, and facilities requirements.
