2.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Reporting of Injuries, Diseases and Dangerous Occurrences Regulations (RIDDOR) 2013</span></div></summary><div class="sc-dqJZss kxJFgY pf-155_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-ctLKXW gOsYRG pf-156_"><div class="sc-feUYzb iXyfoG pf-157_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dWZrec gFZrdc pf-158_"><p class="sc-ePDMnc dIqczD pf-159_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-bffd40ca-edf9-46dd-a935-3d0edc4a8ad9"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Mandates the reporting of workplace accidents and occupational diseases.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details></div></div></div></div><p class="sc-ePDMnc dIqczD pf-162_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-fd0582a7-ff08-4af1-9fdc-33f0503dfce8"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Non-compliance with these regulations can result in:
</span></p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-fbKhWw cWXGnG pf-165_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-leSCGb jlzrdC pf-166_">Legal action and substantial financial penalties
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-leSCGb jlzrdC pf-168_">Increased accident rates and employee injury claims
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-leSCGb jlzrdC pf-170_">Loss of business reputation and customer confidence.
</li></ul><p class="sc-ePDMnc dIqczD pf-172_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-02cb88cf-1040-457e-b767-7fab4d3bf398"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">To minimise risks and improve regulatory alignment, organisations must go beyond basic compliance and adopt strategic, data-driven health and safety management approaches.
</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-feUYzb iXyfoG pf-175_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dWZrec gFZrdc pf-176_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-YysaK ejlKKG pf-177_">The compliance challenge - Addressing workplace safety risks head-on</h3><p class="sc-ePDMnc dIqczD pf-179_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-71e5ccfb-8235-4a28-a8ba-2c82ef1b2301"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Workplaces today are evolving rapidly, introducing new risks, regulatory updates, and operational challenges. Some of the key obstacles organisations face include:
</span></p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-fbKhWw cWXGnG pf-182_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-leSCGb jlzrdC pf-183_"><strong>Managing compliance in high-risk industries</strong> - Sectors like healthcare, construction, and manufacturing require continuous risk assessment due to high exposure to hazards.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-leSCGb jlzrdC pf-185_"><strong>Lack of integrated compliance systems</strong> - Many organisations rely on disconnected processes, leading to compliance gaps and inefficiencies.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-leSCGb jlzrdC pf-187_"><strong>Policy fatigue</strong> - Some businesses have well-written safety policies but fail to implement and monitor them effectively.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-leSCGb jlzrdC pf-189_"><strong>Inconsistent training and competency management</strong> - Many organisations adopt a reactive approach to training rather than ensuring continuous compliance through structured programs.
</li></ul><p class="sc-ePDMnc dIqczD pf-191_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-4329c0ca-91b7-454c-9c91-8df942b7de00"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">To overcome these challenges, businesses must transition from reactive safety management to a proactive, structured compliance strategy.
</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-feUYzb iXyfoG pf-194_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dWZrec gFZrdc pf-195_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-YysaK ejlKKG pf-196_">The solution - Implementing an integrated compliance management system</h3><p class="sc-ePDMnc dIqczD pf-198_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-4a7cb3a4-1de8-47b8-8ac1-1be1bf1f28f9"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">A robust compliance strategy must integrate risk management, operational workflows, policies, and training programs into a single, streamlined framework.
</span></p><div class="sc-hMBXSR dZURqy pf-201_ pf-icon-right" data-scroll-to-top="true" data-open-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3"><details class="sc-iEkSjT crZUoC pf-202_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-gPDJyv guexUq pf-203_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="e827b8ca-c11b-41bf-9f28-f9d66a93df82" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Risk assessments and hazard management</span></div></summary><div class="sc-dqJZss kxJFgY pf-205_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-ctLKXW gOsYRG pf-206_"><div class="sc-feUYzb iXyfoG pf-207_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dWZrec gFZrdc pf-208_"><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-fbKhWw cWXGnG pf-209_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-leSCGb jlzrdC pf-210_">Conduct routine risk assessments and update them regularly.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-leSCGb jlzrdC pf-212_">Implement hierarchical controls (Eliminate → Reduce → Isolate → Control → PPE → Training).
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-leSCGb jlzrdC pf-214_">Align workflows with HSE compliance standards to prevent incidents before they occur.
</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-iEkSjT crZUoC pf-216_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-gPDJyv guexUq pf-217_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="6a93df82-8668-46b4-b784-c1d6cd008615" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Embedding compliance into operational systems
</span></div></summary><div class="sc-dqJZss kxJFgY pf-219_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-ctLKXW gOsYRG pf-220_"><div class="sc-feUYzb iXyfoG pf-221_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dWZrec gFZrdc pf-222_"><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-fbKhWw cWXGnG pf-223_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-leSCGb jlzrdC pf-224_">Integrate HSE compliance tracking into daily business operations.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-leSCGb jlzrdC pf-226_">Use automated compliance monitoring tools to detect potential risks early.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-leSCGb jlzrdC pf-228_">Centralise compliance documentation to ensure audit readiness.
</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-iEkSjT crZUoC pf-230_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-gPDJyv guexUq pf-231_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="cd008615-fe43-4312-b5f0-ca985bbc1eee" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Policy development and compliance procedures
</span></div></summary><div class="sc-dqJZss kxJFgY pf-233_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-ctLKXW gOsYRG pf-234_"><div class="sc-feUYzb iXyfoG pf-235_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dWZrec gFZrdc pf-236_"><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-fbKhWw cWXGnG pf-237_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-leSCGb jlzrdC pf-238_">Ensure all policies align with current HSE regulations.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-leSCGb jlzrdC pf-240_">Make health and safety policies accessible to all employees.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-leSCGb jlzrdC pf-242_">Implement workflow-based compliance procedures to ensure policy adherence.
</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-iEkSjT crZUoC pf-244_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-gPDJyv guexUq pf-245_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="5bbc1eee-5a21-4b60-9475-07757fd3b9c7" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Training and competency development
